name: Precitech Industries
overview: Established in the year 2001, we, “Precitech Industries”, located at Vadagaon Khurd, Sinhgad Road, Pune, are highly appreciated by the clients for manufacturing & supplying a wide range of Dowel Pins, Bushes, Spacers and Washers, Piston Rods, CNC Turned components, Shafts, Drain plugs, Dies & Pillar sets, Rollers & Pulleys, Sleeves, Threaded Studs, Coupling Fittings, SPM Components, Toll Room Components, etc. All our offered products are fabricated using supreme quality of raw material that is procured from some of the authentic and certified vendors of the market. Appreciated among clients for their high durability, corrosion resistance, robust construction, compact design, low maintenance and optimum finish, these are designed at par with the set industry standards. The products offered by us are available in various dimensions, sizes and patterns as per the variegated requirements of our esteemed clients.
